Sylvie Joly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sylvie_Joly 0 Sylvie Joly (18 October 1934 – 4 September 2015) was a French actress and comedian. She was best known for her roles in the films Going Places (1974) and Get Out Your Handkerchiefs (1978). Sylvie_Joly ( 18_October_1934 – 4_September_2015 ) was a_French_actress_and_comedian .
